The adventure continues for 14-year-old tech genius Hiro and his compassionate,
cutting-edge robot Baymax. If dealing with the academic pressure of being the
new kid at the prestigious San Fransokyo Institute of Technology weren't enough,
it's off campus where things really get tricky. Hiro and Baymax, along with
their friends Wasabi, Honey Lemon, Go Go and Fred, unite to form the legendary
superhero team Big Hero 6, protecting their city from a colorful array of
scientifically-enhanced villains intent on creating chaos and mayhem!

Produced by Disney Television Animation.

Go Go and Fred dive deep into comic book mythology to
defeat High Voltage, a mother-daughter supervillain duo.
